{"tid":1105424,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"七人車東廊炒壆甩轆 曼迷涉酒駕被捕","createTime":"2019-04-14T01:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T12:15:46.000Z","uid":186071,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1e0105dce693084fb7b65df0a08ccd4a7535dfc8","tid":1105424,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T01:42:24.000Z","msg":"凌晨零時許，一輛豐田七人車沿東區走廊東行，近太古城一個右彎，疑天雨路滑失控，撞向石壆打白鴿轉，右前輪甩脫及氣袋彈出，衝前100米才停下，車頭嚴重損毀。<br />\n<br />\n身穿英超球隊「紅魔鬼」曼聯球衣的27歲姓馮司機，自行離開車廂，腳及頭受輕傷。警方到場調查，他接受酒精呼氣測試，酒精度數超標，涉嫌酒後駕駛被捕，送往東區醫院治理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PfxuhW6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPfxuhW6.png&h=9bac49a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曼迷 真係馬路炸陣黎"},{"pid":"2549964cecdec8b86964ea650339d6b46bda4e9d","tid":1105424,"uid":122430,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T01:46:44.000Z","msg":"理撚得你，三分已袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea32a28cc134246f7ca7e90418307e8cd50bb0d8","tid":1105424,"uid":36238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T01:48:20.000Z","msg":"爆炸頭去咗魯能之後改埋姓馮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada7217baa4789777f1bc6b02af1e51ada84c13c","tid":1105424,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:09:00.000Z","msg":"咪屈，得拉車係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d44f1b796e32279b5d79f3a07b5800de7b14cf","tid":1105424,"uid":124020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:10:15.000Z","msg":"@拉xxx"},{"pid":"8bcd1a8ec4f7f84f08d010481928696cc0ff87e6","tid":1105424,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:12:17.000Z","msg":"XX福特"},{"pid":"b18fc7a9ff008c89cb843a6485baa1a9e9e414a2","tid":1105424,"uid":9708,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\